OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Belsen showed me how low  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmankind can sink'          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ian Forsyth, one of the first soldiers 
OL,6, to arrive at the liberation of the     
OL,7, Bergen-Belsen concentration camp in    
OL,8, World War Two, has died at the age of  
OL,9, 97.                                    
OL,11,FLast year, he told BBC Scotland that   
OL,12,Fwhat he saw that day had haunted him   
OL,13,Ffor 75 years.                          
OL,15,F"For the first time I realised just how
OL,16,Flow mankind can sink," Mr Forsyth said.
OL,18,FAlthough he was still a young man when 
OL,19,Fhe reached the Northern Germany        
OL,20,Fconcentration camp in April 1945, he   
OL,21,Fhad seen a lot of action.              
